data.name: ReadOfficeOfficeAddress1
data.value: select T1.OFFICE_ID, T1.MAIN_PHONE_NUMBER, T1.TYPE_CODE, T1.NAME, T1.EFFECTIVE_DATE, T1.DISCONTINUE_DATE, T1.MAIN_PHONE_AREA_CD, T1.OFF_OFFICE, T2.TYPE, T2.CITY from CKT_OFFICE T1 join CKT_OFFICE_ADDRESS T2 on (T1.NAME >= @name) and (T1.OFFICE_ID = T2.OFF_GENERATED_ID) and (T2.CITY >= @city) order by T2.CITY, T1.OFFICE_ID, T2.TYPE
